{"tid":1969474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：駐尼日利亞大使非鞠躬道歉 實為俯身觀看短片","createTime":"2020-04-12T12:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T14:04:23.000Z","uid":21470,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"41409e521acf4f5583b4b6bcc683b3cef848e3bc","tid":1969474,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:28:48.000Z","msg":"尼日利亞都識撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國大使館澄清駐尼日利亞大使非鞠躬道歉<br />\n12.04.2020 20:18<br />\n<br />\n中國駐尼日利亞大使周平劍，前日應約會見尼日利亞眾議長巴賈比亞米拉期間，俯身看視頻的片段，被傳為&ldquo;鞠躬道歉&rdquo;。中國大使館發表聲明澄清，指疫情期間為保持社交距離，尼日利亞方面將播放視頻的手機，平放在茶几上，對會見場景的其他解讀都不符合事實。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指， 周平劍當時強調中方防疫人員行為正當，並無不妥。中國政府對所有外國在華人員一視同仁，反對任何針對特定人群的差異性做法，對歧視性言行更是零容忍，在華外國人亦應嚴格遵守當地防疫規定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280373&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280373%26csid%3D261_341&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=9f85e46d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280373&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b2f3709c449866676069b2c54bfabd191a997673","tid":1969474,"uid":16057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"你知 我知 鞠躬果個都知 比人鞠躬果個都知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a0dce825af084874353a2ce73401d27fa3727b","tid":1969474,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:35:17.000Z","msg":"咁細張契仔點睇"},{"pid":"7a3d9e28a9d8776988f26cc70eb86c3d2e5fec54","tid":1969474,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/195752